          "name": "tool_2",
          "rows": [
            {
              "name": "title",
              "value": "SHARE how you feel",
              "_translations": {
                "value": {
                  "tz_sw": true
                }
              },
              "type": "set_variable",
              "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_2.title"
            },
            {
              "name": "text_1",
              "value": "This is hard. Many of us were told not to cry, or show our feelings to our children. But take a deep breath and calmly tell them how you feel. They will understand better, and also learn from you how to deal with stress.",
              "_translations": {
                "value": {
                  "tz_sw": true
                }
              },
              "type": "set_variable",
              "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_2.text_1"
            }
          ],
          "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_2"
        },
        {
          "type": "nested_properties",
          "name": "tool_3",
          "rows": [
            {
              "name": "title",
              "value": "SHOW them you care",
              "_translations": {
                "value": {
                  "tz_sw": true
                }
              },
              "type": "set_variable",
              "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_3.title"
            },
            {
              "name": "text_1",
              "value": "This is also hard! Stress makes us focus on ourselves. But our teens need our support. Ask them how they feel. Listen to them and comfort them. Try a hug or say ‘I understand’. It can change everything.",
              "_translations": {
                "value": {
                  "tz_sw": true
                }
              },
              "type": "set_variable",
              "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_3.text_1"
            }
          ],
          "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_3"
        },
        {
          "type": "nested_properties",
          "name": "tool_4",
          "rows": [
            {
              "name": "title",
              "value": "SEEK the positive",
              "_translations": {
                "value": {
                  "tz_sw": true
                }
              },
              "type": "set_variable",
              "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_4.title"
            },
            {
              "name": "text_1",
              "value": "Can you and your teen think about ideas that might help? Can you do something positive together to take your mind off the stress?",
              "_translations": {
                "value": {
                  "tz_sw": true
                }
              },
              "type": "set_variable",
              "_nested_name": "essential_tools.tool_4.text_1"
            }
